[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "“美好的结局，并非总是需要一路颠沛流离衬托……”",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "“……我喜欢分析员，我最喜欢分析员。”",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "少女一口气写完的誓词在我的手上，我截取她誓词的片段读出声时，那一字一句含在嘴里好似有着蜜糖般的甜味。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "以前都不知道芬妮还有这样可爱的一面啊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我的目光完全无法从眼前灌注了爱意的文字移开。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她的字很灵巧，很飘逸，也很凌厉，带着狮子特有的轻盈和凶狠，可那些文字在我眼中又好似是一只只蝴蝶翩翩起舞。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "明明早就过了春天，却像是见到它们在花丛中飞舞，幽幽香气扑鼻而来，浸透灵魂。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "回过神来，张牙舞爪的纤细影子撞了过来，带着她身上的香气一起。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "笨蛋笨蛋，笨蛋分析员，你……你还给我！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我将手臂伸直，将誓词高高藏在身后。她在我的身前努力踮起脚尖，明明是只狮子，却像是大白兔蹦蹦跳跳，晃晃悠悠。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不过以天启者的身体素质，想要从我手中抢走这份誓词，其实很简单吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我当做没发现她的“礼让”。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "芬妮问了我问题，那也回答我一个问题。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你说。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "芬妮愣了一下，停住争抢的动作，她双手抱住胸口，斜睨着我，金子一样柔顺头发束成的双马尾活泼垂洒。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "普通的人随便触碰狮子是会被咬的，可我还是忍不住去触碰，抚摸狮子的毛发。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她任由我抓住她的头发，她金色的“尾巴”，目光盯着我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我想问，前几天收到作为礼物的戒指时，芬妮在想什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "大概…什么都没想。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "什么……都没想？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是的。我什么都没有想，只是在高兴。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……因为我不用去经历漫长的煎熬去等待答案，我只要等待幸福降临在我身边。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她轻声嘟囔着，明明刚刚被我拥紧在怀里展现了所有的羞涩，可再提起时还是会娇羞。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是吗？我也一样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "什么一样？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "高兴的心情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哼。你当然也该高兴的，本小姐这样闪耀的大明星，死心塌地地爱上了你一人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是啊，你说的没错。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "虽然面前没有镜子，但我脸上的笑容应该是掩饰不住的吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "过去的某一刻开始，我察觉到了她的心思，发现她在蹑手蹑脚，小心翼翼向我接近。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "原本我以为她的性子会是风风火火地闯进来的，可后来想明白了，这样才更符合她的性格。狮子捕猎的时候就是这样，小心翼翼接近，然后一击必杀凶猛凌厉。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可对我而言，爱上一只狮子，靠近她的过程，其实和她接近我的过程是一样的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "笨蛋亲爱的，你不是已经知道答案了吗，为什么还要多问一遍，不难为情吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就是因为芬妮会难为情，才要多问，不然怎么能看到你这副可爱模样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "亲爱的又在捉弄人！哼，不过可爱对狮子来说可算不上赞赏。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她很不实诚地伸手拨了拨自己的马尾，竭力压着嘴边的笑，继续盯着我手中的卡片。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "还有！问题问完了吧，问完了就把誓词还给我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我看着我家小狮子双眼睁得滚圆，盯住我手中小小的纸片。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不对。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我在要将誓词放下前，忽然反应过来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我好像没说你回答完问题，我就把誓词还你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哈？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "因为芬妮脸颊染着酡红的模样太可爱，我还想要继续逗弄她。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她银牙紧咬，好像下一刻要扑上来，可猛地她停下脚步，扭过头去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "算了，本小姐……今天给你点好处怎么样？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就当是笨蛋亲爱的，刚才让我开心的报酬……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……我们来用游戏一决胜负吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "游戏？什么游戏？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "看看谁的忍耐度更强，要是我能忍住，你没忍住的话，就把誓词给我……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她的声音越来越低，脸颊的红晕越来越深。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这下，轮到我呆滞了。虽然芬妮的游戏说明有些没头没尾，但我却毫无阻碍地理解了她的意思。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你确定，要这样做？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我好像是看到一只不知天高地厚的小奶猫，努力抬起双爪，奶声奶气对我挑衅。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你不会是怕了吧？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 71,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你……怎么停下了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 72,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我，我还没输……！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 73,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我输了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 74,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哼，分析员这么快就忍不住了吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 75,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是啊，再继续下去，会忍不住。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 76,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "笨，笨蛋，你这样说……不会……不会害臊吗。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 77,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "什么害臊？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 78,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我指了指自己胸口——指向胸口下狂跳的心脏。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 79,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "芬妮原地宕机许久，才忽地呜叫了一声，扑到我怀里，羞恼地用小拳头捶我胸口。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 80,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "亲爱的是坏蛋！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 81,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在接受分析员的心意之前，我还有些话想要对分析员说。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 82,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "其实在几天之前，我都一直在害怕，在担心，这是一场梦，一个幻象。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 83,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在我真正触及到的时候就会丢下我，消散不见。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 84,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可就在前几天，你找到了傻乎乎以为在为了幸福独自努力的我，牵住我的手，拥抱我，重新给了我勇气，告诉我——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 85,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我并非是在独自追逐着你的身影，我一直在被幸福包裹着。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 86,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "原来美好的结局，并非总是需要一路颠沛流离衬托。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 87,
